data.description: Here's your chance to own a little piece of Heaven.  I say heaven because this home boost one level living with 3 bedrooms, 1 bath that has been fully remodeled so nothing has to be done inside which gives you the ability to enjoy the outside with the Largent Bend fishing access a short trip down the road to recreate. This property also has a second lot the same size as the lot with a house to build a shop or any additional space for storage outside.  Call Jennifer Benski at (406) 590-2099, or your real estate professional.
